titleStmt.title: More news from the fleet being a brief and true account of the late noble and heroick exploit, performed against the Dutch, on the 8th, 9th, and 10th of this present month of August, by Captain Sr. Robert Holmes, Sr. Philip Howard, and Sr. William Jennings ... tune is The King enjoyes his own again.

notesStmt.note: The engagement described occurred August, 1666. Cf. The Historian's Guide, or, England's Remembrancer, London, 1690--p. 60.
Date of publication suggested by Wing.
Reproduction of original in Bodleian Library.
